### 1) Registrar proveedor
POST http://localhost:5002/api/providers/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Proveedor Valdez",
  "pais": "CL",
  "email": "proveedor@correo.com",
  "telefono": "987654321"
}

### 2) Login proveedor
POST http://localhost:5002/api/providers/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "proveedor@correo.com"
}

### Guarda el token aquí:
@token = PON_AQUI_EL_TOKEN

### 3) Crear tienda
POST http://localhost:5002/api/stores
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nombre": "Valdez Store",
  "pais": "CL",
  "idioma": "es",
  "moneda": "CLP",
  "descripcion": "Tienda oficial de Valdez"
}

### 4) Crear producto
POST http://localhost:5002/api/products
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "store_id": 1,
  "nombre": "Aceite Premium 5W30",
  "descripcion": "Aceite sintético de alta calidad",
  "precio": 19990,
  "stock": 50,
  "sku": "ACE-5W30-VALDEZ",
  "imagenes": [
    "https://cdn.com/aceite1.jpg",
    "https://cdn.com/aceite2.jpg"
  ]
}

### 5) Ver productos de la tienda
GET http://localhost:5002/api/products/store/1

### 6) Ver producto completo
GET http://localhost:5002/api/products/1

### 7) Agregar stock
POST http://localhost:5002/api/products/1/add-stock
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cantidad": 20,
  "motivo": "Reposición de inventario"
}

### 8) Quitar stock
POST http://localhost:5002/api/products/1/remove-stock
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "cantidad": 5,
  "motivo": "Venta presencial"
}

### 9) Actualizar producto
PUT http://localhost:5002/api/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "precio": 17990,
  "descripcion": "Aceite sintético premium"
}

### 10) Eliminar producto
DELETE http://localhost:5002/api/products/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 11) Ver tiendas del proveedor
GET http://localhost:5002/api/stores/provider/all
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 12) Ver perfil del proveedor
GET http://localhost:5002/api/providers/me
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
